question.title: APIException 9011 and 9010 error in Places SDK
question.body:
I am new to Android Development and I am learning Maps SDK for Android.

My API key for Maps SDK is working fine and I am able to see Map on my screen with a marker. But the problem is, I am not able to use the Place Autocomplete service and facing the following two errors:

  1. APIException code 9011
  2. APIException code 9010

Here my Places SDK is not working though I have enabled it while creating API Key. I have searched about these two errors but yet I am unable to find the reason for the above-mentioned errors. Why is this happening with me?
